The paper proposes a method for face liveness detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The method involves detecting face liveness based on client identity, which is related to computer security (cs.CR). The use of Siamese network for training the model involves deep learning techniques (cs.MM). The paper also involves experimentation and evaluation of the proposed method, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
